# User Configuration Template

Copy to `CLAUDE.local.md` (gitignored) and fill in your values:

```bash
cp CLAUDE.local.md.template CLAUDE.local.md
```

## Required Variables

```
{USERNAME}         = your.username       # Example: john.smith
{USER_UID}         = your-tdx-user-uid  # Find via: Ask Claude "What's my TDX user UID?"
{RELEASE_VERSION}  = 12.1                # Current release version
```

## Ticket Selection

When asking "get me a ticket", use report "All Open Tickets"
